		<section data-mw-section-id="-1" id="mwLQ" aria-labelledby="Featured_Travel_Topic"><h2 style="font-size:1.25em;" id="Featured_Travel_Topic" class="mw-html-heading"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//en.wikivoyage.org/wiki/Previous_Featured_travel_topics" title="Previous Featured travel topics">Featured Travel Topic</a></h2>
